data.value: RetentionGUI is a Graphical User Interface for the Retention Service. This service watches a directory and checks to see what the creation date was then Deturmins the age of the files to the current date if this age is greater then the "DaysToKeep" variable the files are deleted. This software was writen for use in instances where files accumulate forever. Like Log files and Backups. This software will only allow the age specified to be kept in the assigned directory.
